Then $AC_k = |2 - 2 \omega^k| = 2 |1 - \omega^k|$ and
\[BC_k = |-2 - 2 \omega_k| = 2 |1 + \omega^k|.\]Since $\omega^7 = -1,$ we can also write this as
\[BC_k = 2 |1 - \omega^{k + 7}|.\]Therefore,
